channel.title: Good DeltaScape Client?
channel.description:
Does anybody know a good client I can use for my DeltaScape Source server. I downloaded the DeltaScape Source. I'm going to code it, although I need a good client that is updated and has the most updated items and etc. If you can provide the name and the download link, or where\how to download it. Also please make sure the client's editable. Thankyou.
Sincerely, 2xbladex2

item.title: Good DeltaScape Client?
item.dc:creator: @wwe4eva wwe4eva
item.description:
@wwe4eva wrote:

www.files.filefront.com/DeltaScape+v16+clientrar/;11614333;/fileinfo.html That Should Work.

His Clients Are Editable ^.- Also, that has the box for the ip, enter your user, pass, then hit enter, then type the ip. Voila.
